{"tid":1307692,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"只有武力可以阻止暴力 而唔係暴力令暴力產生","createTime":"2019-07-11T16:22:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-12T11:00:31.000Z","uid":167938,"like":77,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1a95ec9aa7fe5d318c13187110935888ea6b0d81","tid":1307692,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:22:51.000Z","msg":"有人會話 「暴力只會產生更多暴力」<br />\n錯了<br />\n<br />\n我話「只有武力可以阻止暴力」<br />\n<br />\n否則警察唔需要有鎗<br />\n美國國旗上唔會有原子彈<br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭唔需要被俄國吞拼克里米亞<br />\n因為佢有3000粒核彈<br />\n<br />\n立法會亦都唔需要衝擊<br />\n林鄭都會壽終正寢<br />\n<br />\n再係咁落去<br />\n香港人亦永遠打唔贏共產黨<br />\n呢句 唔需要負評我 我係咪鬼你自己起底"},{"pid":"fa8c5f90178160c7ec5e418922a7d120b5482b1c","tid":1307692,"uid":124859,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:23:43.000Z","msg":"左膠禍港 見死不救"},{"pid":"70b6c3b12e06ec51fb096941fc47a0e9c9533e03","tid":1307692,"uid":151057,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"香港人可以有咩武力 馴化曬"},{"pid":"84a08fa25ac10c328ee9853727f06e90fa3ad7cf","tid":1307692,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"十連我無野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c4fdc0026dabdc34edbcd643f7808b3e8d496f12","tid":1307692,"uid":167938,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"70b6c3b12e06ec51fb096941fc47a0e9c9533e03","tid":1307692,"uid":151057,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:24:00.000Z","msg":"香港人可以有咩武力 馴化曬"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:24:58.000Z","msg":"歷史上不少以弱勝強既case<br />\n我有計我做左<br />\n<br />\n但係首先係心態唔可以再<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和平</span></span>"},{"pid":"9deb7c365504e32571b8a249bbc918e339250ea5","tid":1307692,"uid":243380,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:25:27.000Z","msg":"事實喎<br />\n用愛與和平去感化敵人<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"