g\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqsyFntG.jpg&h=e3c7f386&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"920fdc866f4f1d5f03082d2b95940f797d3ae909","tid":1307692,"uid":144466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:39:22.000Z","msg":"民意唔係咁睇！<br />\n村民唔係咁諗！<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a69ab22a50be20d6daf810377e0802d6bc1d1c2e","tid":1307692,"uid":2429,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:39:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0bNFY6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0bNFY6E.jpg&h=0e3ff068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/POJqqMr.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPOJqqMr.jpg&h=d5937562&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yUnCgTg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyUnCgTg.jpg&h=4d401a96&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0KAgxru.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0KAgxru.jpg&h=a97e178b&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GmUtoye.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGmUtoye.jpg&h=36d1db08&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1gBzi6w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1gBzi6w.jpg&h=067ee06f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n堅持五大訴求，不撤不散︰<br />\n<br />\n一、撤回修例<br />\n二、撤回6.12暴動定性<br />\n三、撤銷所有反送中抗爭者控罪<br />\n四、責成獨立調查委員會追究警方濫暴<br />\n五、實行真雙普選"},{"pid":"f9cef7da3c307323bfa93ee813cf4931eff430cc","tid":1307692,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:46:17.000Z","msg":"在我而言<br />\n武力同暴力在於其 目的前設<br />\n<br />\n前者為阻止你而做<br />\n後者為達到私人目的而做<br />\n<br />\n兩者手段上係一致<br />\n只係原則唔同<br />\n<br />\n例如當年日皇以暴力手段 去達致一統天下既目的<br />\n係暴力<br />\n<br />\n當年美軍以原子彈殺十萬人 係達致阻止上面呢個目的而做<br />\n<br />\n兩者都係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">殺人</span>"},{"pid":"024ac4f9e5b475755a5ca1b2c53e1d9329245aec","tid":1307692,"uid":252321,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T16:47:07.000Z","msg":"老老實實，條肥鳩最後畀人拉咗兼落charge，幾乎真係萬中無一嘅例子：<br />\n<br />\n-太誇張，連打十幾拳，仲要打頭 (平時啲藍絲廢老通常打一兩拳)<br />\n-肥鳩打完人仲戇鳩鳩企喺度等拉 (平時啲藍絲廢老通常打完就走，邊會企定定等黑警嚟)<br />\n-條肥鳩自己戇鳩，認自己打人<br />\n-差佬食錯藥 / 撞正真正政治中立嘅警察 (我諗而家應該真係唔多)<br />\n<br />\n藍衫義士係值得欣賞，但係我絕對唔建議大家效法；佢嘅作用係類似以死明志嘅烈士，一個都嫌多，講完<br />\n<br />\n畀人打完一拳點算？<br />\n人多就圍佢，睇下想公民遞捕定係還拖爽完就走（如果選擇後者就要小心周圍有冇CCTV）<br />\n人少又覺得自己打唔贏，真係走為上著"},{"pid":"62f18402c7d163193905b05944aa4c9524463eda","tid":1307692,"uid":167938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T17:00:11.000Z","msg":"我知你地啲撚屌香港人一定有睇到我呢個post<br />\n但你咪唔去面對呢件事 唔代表呢啲事會自己消失 亦都唔代表你有解決方案"}]}